start
declare variables, num1, num2, product, difference, quotient, and sum
read values num1 and num2
add num1 and num2 and assign the result to sum
subtract num1 and num2 and assign the result to difference
divide num1 and num2 and assign the result to quotient
multiply num1 and num2 and assign the result to product
display sum, difference, quotient, and product
stop
